uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.collection

Interface IntStreamDecorator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BaseStream<Integer,IntStream>, BaseStreamDecorator<Integer,IntStream>, IntStream
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceStream.IntResourceStream

    public interface IntStreamDecorator
extends BaseStreamDecorator<Integer,IntStream>, IntStream
    A decorator for an IntStream which wraps intermediate and terminal operations such that they can be easily extended.
